Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,葵小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自那以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已经两年了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,花菱少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,起得早了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 让我在旁边小睡一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,千、千香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千、千香！？你为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,薰…薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不、不是 不是的 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 不 说不是并不是指那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事呀？怎么有人大叫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,千香！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,唉唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在学长的被窝里的呀？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为昨晚太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,千香的话 可以原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那么晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 千香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 房东小姐今天起得也很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…只是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是星期天 安安心心多睡点不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是星期天呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我都搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的早餐也很丰盛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不淡不咸 还是一样绝妙的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,凉拌油花菜 是时鲜菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,研究院那边怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,研究生和大学时代不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,此外 虽然考虑需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果不是建立在正视将来的基础上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千香 nice timing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,管理员小姐的话好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,千香 自己的事要自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,报告还没写完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥还真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐们喜欢哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间说些什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就、就是 千香 还以为你要说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我又未问什么奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是、是怎么样的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？讨厌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千、千香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,千香真是天真无邪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 好想回答「喜欢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,葵小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想说「最喜欢薰少爷」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,「因为我是薰少爷的未婚妻」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 好像没米了 必须去买
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但米很重 最好和谁一起去买
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样嘛 怎么样嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说了现在很忙了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,忙死了 忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 妙子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,报告怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 还在苦战中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明天还不完成的话 教授会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,研究生还真是够忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 有什么事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不 不是什么很急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你就努力写报告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不能打扰薰少爷学习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,花菱少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小茧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,茧来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你做什么 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是住这里 每天都来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想什么时候来是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么理由啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个性格真是一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的粗鲁才是越来越厉害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为今后还是应该\N考虑一下樱百货的独立市场调查计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那么在明天的干部职员会议上再谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沏了红茶 可以进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅姐姐喜欢大哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 喜欢或是讨厌不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 薰少爷就是大家的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 刚才葵小姐一个人出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天呢 想去那个新开的意大利店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,意大利啊 不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在学长面前的时候化点妆试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说归说 又没有什么高级的化妆品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前一阵子好像买了新的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,千香…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐 这个是用来决胜负的内衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看 借我穿穿 给我摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 千香 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不能使劲拉的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,撕裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,睡个午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 千香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太纠缠不休啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢大哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和薰没任何关系 只是个学生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是、是、是、是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,回答就是没任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,关系非常好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂、蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,千香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,甚、什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把耳朵凑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你把这件事说给其他人听的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是 千香对谁…谁也不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 吃拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 小茧姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不是说了现在很忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个游戏 那个野蛮女人都行\N我怎么可能不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 反正小茧姐姐的答案我知道\N不回答也没什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在做些什么啊！过门女婿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么呀？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,果然重了点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我来拿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,果然在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是草莓云呢拿味的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看呀看呀 薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,壁橱好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然用来考虑的时间很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果不是建立在正视将来的基础上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,将来…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,写报告这么忙还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,休息也是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵想住什么样的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很像呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和薰少爷以往的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从那以后已经过了两年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们的再次相见…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 是从小葵来开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的家都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是多小的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和薰少爷在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 千香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵姐姐是怎么想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对大哥哥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,千香知道「缘」这个字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,「缘」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,「缘」就是联系人与人的缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 过门女婿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所有现在在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,都互相被「缘」联结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会相见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当然千香和我们也有「缘」相连接哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以觉得自己和薰少爷\N从很久很久以前就以「缘」相联了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,薰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,千香好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了谁喜欢大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,千香…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,千香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,千香也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但最喜欢的人是茧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是茧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,脸看起来好红呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快点吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,茧要坐在花菱少爷的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小茧 不要随便换位子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想坐什么是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！？顽固的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像被清新的风儿抚过\N逐渐堆积起来的樱花花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,温柔地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,织结出重要的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 青出于蓝～缘～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,葵会一直在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,永远地
